  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK607">
<l>iṭipurin teḷḷuñcol kēṭpar maṭipurintu </l>
<l>māṇṭa vuñaṟṟi lavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who through idleness, and do not engage themselves in dignified exertion, will subject themselves to rebukes and reproaches.</l>
            </lg>
